{"name": "multimapping", "metadata": {"name": "MultiMapping", "version": "5.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 6 - Mature", "Environment :: Web Environment", "Framework :: Zope :: 5", "License :: OSI Approved :: Zope Public License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: CPython", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: PyPy"], "home_page": "https://github.com/zopefoundation/MultiMapping", "license": "ZPL 2.1", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["ExtensionClass"], "summary": "Special MultiMapping objects used in Zope.", "upload_time": 1675938315}, "documentation": ["Overview\n========\n\nMultiMapping provides special objects used in some Zope2 internals like ZRDB.\n\nChangelog\n=========\n\n5.0 (2023-02-09)\n----------------\n\n- Drop support for Python 2.7, 3.4, 3.5, 3.6.\n\n- Add support for Python 3.8, 3.9, 3.10, 3.11.\n\n\n4.1 (2018-10-05)\n----------------\n\n- Add support for Python 3.7.\n\n4.0 (2017-05-17)\n----------------\n\n- Add `__contains__` support.\n\n- Remove the Python 2-only C extension.\n\n3.1 (2017-04-26)\n----------------\n\n- Add support for Python 3.6, drop support for Python 2.6.\n\n3.0 (2016-04-03)\n----------------\n\n- Update compatibility to Python 3.4/3.5.\n\n- Add a pure-Python implementation used for Python 3 and Pypy.\n\n- Rewrote tests as unit tests.\n\n2.13.0 (2010-03-30)\n-------------------\n\n- Released as separate package.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "MultiMapping", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "MultiMapping.pyMultiMapping", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "MultiMapping.MultiMapping", "bases": ["Base"], "methods": [{"